!! Missing the Mark
When we miss the mark, that is called Sin. We have failed to do what He has told us to do or by doing what He has told us what we should not do.

Sin results in death. What is the basis of our beliefs. This is what God has taken to us.

<<<
And the LORD God commanded the man, saying "You may surely eat of every tree of the garden, but of the tree of the knowledge of good and evil you shall not eat, for in the day that you eat of it, you shall surely die."
<<<
Genesis 2:16-17

Thus we know the story. They ate of the tree and they ultimately died.

Just - "Based on doing what is morally right and fair."

!! Eternal Condemnation for Those Who are Sinners
<<<
[Jesus said] "Then he [Son of Man] will say to those on his left, 'Depart from me, you cursed, into the eternal fire prepared for the devil and his angels.
<<<
Matthew 25:41

We have all been born in sin. The original sin: "the corruption of the human race."

"If the fruit is corrupted we must look to the tree as the root of the problem." R. C. Sproul

All their children are born of the same seed and thus corrupted.

<<<
Behold, I was brought forth in iniquity, and in sin did my mother conceive me.
<<<
Psalm 51:5

All of the children born of the slave, they were born of the master. He was now the one to whom they had to submit. All who were born after them, were also themselves, slaves.

<<<
and we were by nature children of wrath, like the rest of mankind.
<<<
Ephesians 2:3

Deuteronomy 28:1-2; Deuteronomy 28:15

