!! Judgement Day
The consequence that we all face is judgement.

<<<
And just as it is appointed for man to die once, and after that comes judgement.
<<<
Hebrews 9:27

The Bible makes it clear that we will face judgement

!! Verdict
The verdict for each of us is already established and known.

<<<
If you, O LORD, should mark iniquities, O Lord, who could stand?
<<<
Psalm 130:3

<<<
as it is written: "None is righteous, no, not one"
<<<
